WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.400
Hi there, my name is Xintong, I'm a product designer focused on complex user experiences,

00:05.400 --> 00:07.480
with recent work in fintech.

00:07.480 --> 00:12.560
In my work, I often explore different ways a flow could work, compare options, and decide

00:12.560 --> 00:17.720
what should be prioritised or simplified based on business needs and system constraints.

00:17.720 --> 00:23.160
My background is a mix of product design and fine art, which has shaped how I communicate ideas.

00:23.160 --> 00:28.880
I tend to externalise thinking early through sketches and workshops,

00:28.880 --> 00:34.720
so decisions can be shared, discussed, and iterated on with my product and engineer team.

00:34.720 --> 00:40.640
In my portfolio, you'll see examples of how I use flow exploration, visual thinking,

00:40.640 --> 00:44.640
and collaborative workshops to shape and refine product decisions.

00:44.640 --> 00:47.360
I do hope you enjoy reading it, bye now :)
